vaScript/Guide/Using_promises#timing\">Timing</a></p>\n </li>\n <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Iterators_and_Generators\">반복기와 생성기</a>\n  <p><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Iterators_and_Generators#iterators\">Iterators</a><br>\n   <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Iterators_and_Generators#iterables\">Iterables</a><br>\n   <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Iterators_and_Generators#generators\">Generators</a></p>\n </li>\n <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Meta_programming\">메타 프로그래밍</a>\n  <p><code><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Meta_programming#proxies\">프록시(Proxy</a></code><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Meta_programming#proxies\" style=\"font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', monospace; background-color: rgba(234, 239, 242, 0.498039);\">)</a><br>\n   <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Meta_programming#handlers_and_traps\">Handlers와 traps</a><br>\n   <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Meta_programming#revocable_proxy\">Revocable Proxy</a><br>\n   <code><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Meta_programming#reflection\">Reflect</a></code></p>\n </li>\n <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Modules\">JavaScript 모듈</a>\n  <p><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Modules#exporting_module_features\">Exporting</a><br>\n   <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Modules#importing_features_into_your_script\">Importing</a><br>\n   <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Modules#default_exports_versus_named_exports\">Default exports</a><br>\n   <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Modules#renaming_imports_and_exports\">Renaming features</a><br>\n   <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Modules#aggregating_modules\">Aggregating modules</a><br>\n   <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Modules#dynamic_module_loading\">Dynamic module loading</a></p>\n </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    \n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Introduction\">다음  »</a></li>\n</ul><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"목차","id":"목차"}],"summary":"JavaScript 안내서에서 JavaScript 언어 개요와 사용법을 알아보세요. 언어 기능에 대해 상세한 정보가 필요하면 JavaScript 참고서를 방문하세요.","popularity":0.0019,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Guide","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"JavaScript Guide","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Guía de JavaScript","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Guide JavaScript","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"JavaScript ガイド","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Przewodnik JavaScript","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Guia JavaScript","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Руководство JavaScript","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"JavaScript 指南","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"JavaScript 指南","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/javascript/guide","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/javascript/guide/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide","title":"JavaScript 안내서"}],"pageTitle":"JavaScript 안내서 - JavaScript | MDN","noIndexing":false}}